{{Noticebox/Official}}
The '''Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition''' is a limited-edition variant of the Bigscreen Beyond 2e PC VR headset, produced through a partnership between [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]] and [https://www.bigscreenvr.com/ Bigscreen]. It features VRChat-themed industrial design, exclusive packaging, and digital rewards redeemable in VRChat.<ref name="vrc-bsb2e">[https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/announcing-the-bigscreen-beyond-2-vrchat-edition "Announcing the Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition!"] on ''hello.vrchat.com''. Published July 16, 2025. Retrieved April 8, 2026.</ref><ref name="bigscreen-bsb2e">[https://store.bigscreenvr.com/blogs/beyond/introducing-the-bigscreen-beyond-2e-vrchat-edition "Introducing the Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition"] on ''store.bigscreenvr.com''. Retrieved April 8, 2026.</ref>

== Hardware ==
The VRChat Edition is based on the Beyond 2e, a tethered PC VR headset with integrated eye tracking, compatible with SteamVR Lighthouse tracking and accessories.<ref name="vrc-bsb2e" /> The edition adds an exclusive translucent "Atomic Purple" shell and co-designed retail packaging.<ref name="bigscreen-bsb2e" />

== Digital extras ==
Each unit includes three digital rewards redeemable in VRChat:
* A profile [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]] ("Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition Owner")
* An in-app [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|sticker]] ("Seeing Beyond")
* An in-app [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|item]] ("Bigscreen Beyond 2e: VRChat Edition")
