== Availability ==
The VRChat Edition is a limited run, available while supplies last, with a starting price of US$1,269.<ref name="bigscreen-bsb2e" /> Preorders opened on July 16, 2025, with shipments expected from September 2025.<ref name="vrc-bsb2e" /><ref name="bigscreen-bsb2e" />

== In VRChat ==
On September 23, 2025, VRChat announced on [https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com Bluesky] that the edition was featured in the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat Home|VRChat Home]] world.<ref>VRChat ([https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com @vrchat.com]). Bluesky post dated September 23, 2025. Retrieved April 8, 2026.</ref>

